572
00:32:08,799 --> 00:32:10,002
This booklet

573
00:32:10,319 --> 00:32:12,162
is the pinnacle.

574
00:32:13,920 --> 00:32:15,360
However, isn't it more evil

575
00:32:15,510 --> 00:32:16,829
