576
00:32:17,087 --> 00:32:18,087
Your Highness.

577
00:32:19,430 --> 00:32:20,680
Calling them dogs

578
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:22,242
might make them angry

579
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:24,082
but they are just words of scolding.

580
00:32:24,759 --> 00:32:26,242
