00:41:45,159 --> 00:41:46,362
Good morning.

745
00:41:46,920 --> 00:41:48,722
Good morning, everyone.

746
00:41:49,125 --> 00:41:50,322
Good morning!

747
00:41:51,301 --> 00:41:52,301
Lord Fan.

748
00:41:53,629 --> 00:41:56,282
